* Iterator interface that client apps implement to return training examples. When FederatedCompute
 * runs a computation, it will call into this interface to fetech training examples to feed to the
 * computation.
 *
 * @hide

methods.name: void next(@NonNull IteratorCallback callback)
methods.comment: Called when FederatedCompute needs another example.

methods.name: void close()
methods.comment: Called by FederatedCompute when it is done using this iterator instance.
